    <string name="settings_faq_content">FAQ (Frequently Asked Questions)\n\n1. What is NewsApp?\nNewsApp is a news reader that brings the latest stories from trusted sources into one place. Follow the topics you like and read with a clean, comfortable layout.\n\n2. Is NewsApp free?\nYes, NewsApp is free to use. Some advanced features may become premium later, but the core reading experience will stay free.\n\n3. Where do the stories come from?\nNews in NewsApp is curated from online news portals and official media outlets. We strive to show only credible and relevant sources.\n\n4. Why are stories not loading?\nMake sure your internet connection is stable. If the issue persists, try:\n- Close and reopen the app\n- Pull to refresh on the news list\n- Ensure you are on the latest Play Store version\n\n5. Does NewsApp store my personal data?\nNewsApp only stores data needed to run the app (like preferences and favorite topics). We do not share your personal data with third parties without permission.\n\n6. How do I report wrong content or bugs?\nContact us via the Contact us menu in the app. Include a screenshot (if any) and a short description so we can fix it faster.</string>
    <string name="settings_contact_content">Need help or want to share feedback?\nThe NewsApp team is happy to receive your questions, suggestions, or bug reports.\n\nPhone/WhatsApp\n+62 813-8577-0691\n\nEmail\nsupport.newsapp@gmail.com\n\nWe aim to respond to every message on business days from 09:00 \u2013 18:00 WIB.</string>
    <string name="settings_about_content">NewsApp \u2013 The latest news in your hand\n\nNewsApp makes it easy to follow the latest stories without opening many different sites. With a light, easy-to-use design, NewsApp keeps you up to date amid a busy day.\n\nKey features:\n- Fresh news from trusted sources\n- Clean, readable article lists\n- Full-content article details\n- Search and filter by title/topic\n\nNewsApp is continually being improved. Your feedback helps us make the app faster, more comfortable, and more useful for everyone.</string>
